news_header: Kenvue Inc, Nexstar Media Group Inc, and Winmark Corp will trade ex-dividend on 2/12/25, with dividends paid on 2/26/25 and 3/3/25.
news_original_title: Ex-Dividend Reminder: Kenvue, Nexstar Media Group and Winmark
news_text: On February 12, 2025, Kenvue Inc (KVUE), Nexstar Media Group Inc (NXST), and Winmark Corp (WINA) will trade ex-dividend. Kenvue will pay a quarterly dividend of $0.205, Nexstar will pay $1.86, and Winmark will pay $0.90. Based on their recent stock prices, KVUE is expected to open 1.02% lower, NXST 1.23% lower, and WINA 0.24% lower. Winmark is a contender for the 'Dividend Aristocrats' index with over 14 years of dividend increases. Current estimated annual yields are 4.06% for Kenvue, 4.91% for Nexstar, and 0.95% for Winmark.
